defaultQ153default 
defaultChair:default Two of our witnesses suggested that it would be good to focus on what has actually happened—on outcomes or people’s experience. Is that something that the Department feels would be helpful?
defaultGregory Barker:default Certainly very much so, given that these are novel technologies—well, some of them are not novel, because they have been around for many years, but they are new at scale, in terms of their deployment in the 
defaultUK
